{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>有一个集合M是这样生成的：(1) 已知k是集合M的元素； (2) 如果y是M的元素，那么，2y+1和3y+1都是M的元素；(3) 除了上述二种情况外，没有别的数能够成为M的一个元素。<p><p>问题：任意给定k和x，请判断x是否是M的元素。这里的k是无符号整数，x 不大于 100000，如果是，则输出YES，否则，输出NO。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"判断元素是否存在 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>如果是，则输出 YES，否则，输出NO。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>输入整数 k 和 x, 逗号间隔。<p>","examples":"<input>0,22\n</input><output>YES\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1211","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}